IconArrowDownAndBackComponent extends IconBase

Selector: sbb-icon-arrows-right-left

Properties
Name Description
@Input()

height: string

Height of the icon.
@Input()

size: 'grow' | 'fixed'

Configure the size of the SVG. 'grow' will allow the SVG to grow or shrink to the parent size. 'fixed' will apply the default width and height of the SVG. Defaults to 'grow'.
@Input()

svgClass: ''

The given CSS class or classes will be applied to the SVG element.
@Input()

width: string

Width of the icon.
